snippet.title: Unleashed FPS
snippet.description:
Major update with new multithreaded pathfinding and the added option to switch to the newest GL4 Rendering. This new rendering method allows for 10x more fps when many (1000+) units are on the battlefield.

2 years of full devotion of ivand (GL4 rendering) and the last 6-9 months of Tarnished Knight (MT-pathing) finally are now here for everyone to enjoy.

Read more on this major update in our massive newspost on: https://www.beyondallreason.info/news/groundbreaking-engine-improvements-are-live-multithreaded-pathing-and-new-renderer-deployed
